OORS, SAINIK LAMINATES, CENTURYDOORS, CENTURYPROWUD, CENTURYLAMINATES, CENTURYVENEERS, Zykron, and CENTURYPLY brands. Century Plyboards (India) Limited was incorporated in 1982 and is headquartered in Kolkata, India."}}